===Etymology===
{{Han etyl}}
{{Han compound|戈|口|一|ls=ic}}, "territory".

Borrowed for abstract meanings. The derivative [[國]] and [[域]] refer to the original word.

Note that [[咸]] is not derived from 或, and that the characters 口一 are stacked in the opposite order in these characters. Both are ultimately from {{m|mul|戈||halberd, spear|sc=Hani}}.

